reviewText: If your child loves Diego, I think this is a must-have.  I don't know if my daughter was simply craving new episodes, but the DVD arrived yesterday.  I played it for her and then it was bedtime.  The end... ha!  I found out that her big sister found her awake this  morning at 6am and turned on her tv (with this DVD, and put it on) and when I did not hear from my daughter by 10am I decided to go wake up the sleepy head.  And there she was, in her "Diego coma" laying in bed still.  Happy as could be, did not want to come downstairs --- just wanted to stay there and watch Diego.  So, while I've only half heartedly watched it once, I'll give it five stars from my devoted Diego fan.
summary: My 2 year old LOVES this new video
